# 18. Como montar histórico de eventos

## Base

```text
contrato | anomesdia | evento
---------+-----------+-------------
123      | 20260103  | ENTRADA
123      | 20260211  | ACIONAMENTO
123      | 20260302  | ACORDO
```

## Query

```sql
WITH base AS (
    SELECT
        contrato,
        cast(date_parse(cast(anomesdia AS varchar), '%Y%m%d') AS date) AS dt_evento,
        cast(evento AS varchar) AS evento
    FROM origem
    WHERE evento IS NOT NULL
)
SELECT
    contrato,
    array_agg(
        CAST(
            ROW(dt_evento, evento)
            AS ROW(dt_evento DATE, evento VARCHAR)
        )
        ORDER BY dt_evento
    ) AS hist_eventos
FROM base
GROUP BY contrato;
```

## Contar acordos

```sql
SELECT
    contrato,
    cardinality(
        filter(hist_eventos, x -> x.evento = 'ACORDO')
    ) AS qtd_acordos
FROM contrato_hist;
```

