# 19. Como montar histórico de status

## Query

```sql
WITH base AS (
    SELECT
        contrato,
        substr(cast(anomesdia AS varchar), 1, 6) AS mesref,
        status
    FROM origem
),
foto_mes AS (
    SELECT
        contrato,
        mesref,
        max_by(status, mesref) AS status_mes
    FROM base
    GROUP BY 1, 2
)
SELECT
    contrato,
    array_agg(
        CAST(
            ROW(mesref, status_mes)
            AS ROW(mesref VARCHAR, status VARCHAR)
        )
        ORDER BY mesref
    ) AS hist_status
FROM foto_mes
GROUP BY contrato;
```

## Pegar status atual

```sql
SELECT
    contrato,
    element_at(hist_status, -1).status AS status_atual
FROM contrato_hist;
```

## Montar jornada em string

```sql
SELECT
    contrato,
    array_join(
        transform(hist_status, x -> x.status),
        ' -> '
    ) AS jornada_status
FROM contrato_hist;
```

Resultado exemplo:

```text
OK -> ATRASO -> ACORDO
```

